{
  "stem": "14463.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we want-- my mother and I, we want somewhere to live, right, where to sleep.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Can give us something?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We'll pay you, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was Russians-- you know, a lady, 60, you know, and her husband.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she said, look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I have got no room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But if you-- they all had [NON-ENGLISH], you know, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, there was a house, and there was a front yard.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was a house that way, and a house that way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So it was like a little square.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And with the front door, you know, you couldn't get in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so on the left hand side, he said, there's a cow in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we can divide that in half and you can live in there with your mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Terrific.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we took over these premises.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the cow was on one side and we were on the other side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a little wall in between.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all we had in there was-- the man, you know, the fellow made a [NON-ENGLISH], again, two [INAUDIBLE], and put straw on it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had a little bit of luggage, one little window, this size, looking outside onto the street, right, and one window looking into the yard, to their house.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And their house was a palatial house-- beautiful curtains, white [? yarn. ?] I saw the curtains.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I thought I was going mad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Curtains, with chairs, with-- decked in white, in cloth, and all sort of things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the people were very nice to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we lived in there, together with the cow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then a couple came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A couple came-- a brother and sister, begging us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They've got nowhere to live.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We got them in there too!",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
